What's in a Name?
-----------------

On most online services I'm called h-lame (or hlame if I'm not allowed punctuation 
in the username).  There's a story behind why I chose this name.  It's not a 
particularly brilliant story, but it is a story that I've been asked a few times. 
I figured that if I have a story behind my chosen nom-de-net then others might
too.

That's what this app is for.

Sign in with twitter.
Tell it the story behind your name.
That's it.